        {
            "title": "Super Micro聯合創辦人辭職,「虛假伺服器」走私細節曝光",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8H8YwWPBRcVaBSDkEjFBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_1_M_1440048330.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> Super Micro Computer Inc(納斯達克股票代碼:SMCI)已確認聯合創辦人廖義賢(Yih-Shyan \"Wally\" Liaw)在遭到聯邦起訴後辭去董事會職務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次離職正值解封的起訴書披露了一項據稱價值25億美元的複雜計劃,旨在繞過美國對輝達(NVIDIA Corporation)(納斯達克股票代碼:NVDA)人工智能技術的出口管制。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a8ba89dd-a313-3271-9238-b2e92f9a85c0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為穩定其監管地位,這家伺服器製造商已任命英特爾資深人士、現任全球貿易與制裁副總裁DeAnna Luna擔任代理首席合規官。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>欺騙性物流與「虛假」硬體</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">起訴書詳細描述了一項「複雜的轉運」行動,據稱一名東南亞中間商使用虛假文件掩蓋中國作為最終目的地的事實。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為欺騙調查人員,被告據稱在倉儲設施中使用「虛假」伺服器來分散公司內部合規團隊和美國出口管制官員的注意力,同時將受限制的硬體轉運至中國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">僅在2025年4月下旬至5月中旬期間,這些非法流通就佔了約5.1億美元的銷售額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">廖義賢同時擔任業務發展高級副總裁,在加州北區法院首次出庭後以無擔保保釋金獲釋;正式保釋聽證會定於週三舉行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">董事會現在縮減至八名董事,該公司面臨一項關鍵的「信譽試金石」,因為它試圖證明這些行為是個別人員的不當行為,而非系統性監督失敗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/super-micro%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E8%99%9B%E5%81%87%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8-%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-102858405.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 19:22:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "普京重申莫斯科對德黑蘭的承諾,稱俄羅斯是忠實朋友和可靠夥伴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lLdBaG87BBpyRsw_qunzPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/STOCK-EXCHANGE-RUSSIAN-TRADING-SYSTEMS_M_1440048891.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 俄羅斯總統普京週六在向伊朗領導層發出的諾魯茲節祝賀信中重申了莫斯科對伊朗的承諾,稱克里姆林宮是\"忠實的朋友和可靠的夥伴\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一外交姿態正值德黑蘭的關鍵時刻,伊朗目前正面臨自1979年革命以來最嚴重的地緣政治和經濟危機。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>\"支持缺口\"成為焦點</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管公開展示了團結,但莫斯科實際提供的軍事和經濟援助深度仍是激烈猜測的焦點。來自伊朗消息來源的報導顯示,內部挫折感日益加劇,一些官員聲稱,在德黑蘭面臨不斷升級的外部壓力之際,俄羅斯提供的\"實質幫助很少\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9e42b85-09b5-34d2-807a-664ea8f022c8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">莫斯科被認為的猶豫態度凸顯了夥伴關係中的潛在裂痕,儘管兩國都發現自己越來越被西方金融體系孤立。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對全球市場而言,克里姆林宮官方言論與實際支持現實之間的摩擦是一個關鍵變數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果俄羅斯繼續袖手旁觀,缺乏強大的\"北方緩衝\"可能會使伊朗更容易受到供應鏈中斷的影響,從而影響該地區的貿易穩定性和整個中東的海上保險費率。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>應對戰略孤立</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師認為,普京發出這一信息的時機是試圖在不承諾德黑蘭可能尋求的直接軍事干預的情況下維持外交影響力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著地區利益和全球制裁的影響加劇,克里姆林宮在平衡自身國內需求與中東盟友需求方面的能力,將決定俄伊軸心的長期穩定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%8E%AB%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%B7%E9%BB%91%E8%98%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE-%E7%A8%B1%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%BF%A0%E5%AF%A6%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E5%A4%A5%E4%BC%B4-100956451.html",
